04:00.700 --> 04:02.680
China doesn't pay our tariffs,

04:02.700 --> 04:05.720
American importers do
when they receive Chinese goods

04:05.740 --> 04:08.770
and they usually pass that
cost along to U.S. consumers.

04:08.790 --> 04:11.840
Something that chief economic
adviser, Larry Kudlow,

04:11.870 --> 04:14.740
