when you're sadly eating it

04:39.800 --> 04:41.850
and finally,
two and a half hours later.

04:42.770 --> 04:43.830
You pay three times.

04:44.810 --> 04:48.720
It's an open question whether
Trump knows this, and doesn't care

04:48.750 --> 04:51.830
