15:20.410 --> 15:22.420
Now, look at it from
my point of view.

15:23.280 --> 15:24.320
We can't say.

15:25.500 --> 15:29.440
There's no way I can say
that that is a homicide.

15:29.500 --> 15:33.520
There's no way of telling
how, why this man died.

15:35.360 --> 15:38.520
Except, there is a way
to tell how that man died:

15:39.310 --> 15:41.430
a medical investigation
into his death,

15:41.490 --> 15:44.300
which happens to be
your exact job.

15:44.420 --> 15:47.370
Like hearing a clown say:
"There is no way to twist"

15:47.390 --> 15:49.450
"this balloon into
a shape of a dog or hat."

